oman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;mso-fareast-language:RO\">Atunci\nvei ajunge să nu-ţi mai pese dacă eşti bogat sau sărac, criticat sau slăvit,\nonorat sau dezonorat. Luând parte la moartea lui Isus faţă de tot ce înseamnă\nlumea aceasta, viaţa ta este mai mult ca a lui Isus, ceea ce îţi dă dreptul să\numbli pe acest pământ ca un rege.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#444444;mso-fareast-language:RO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nmajor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;mso-fareast-language:RO\">Îţi\ndoreşti o astfel de viaţă?</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#444444;mso-fareast-language:RO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria, serif; color: black;\"><b>Atunci această carte îţi poate fi de un real